      • ArcadeDriveWithInputs

        public ArcadeDriveWithInputs(double forward,
                     double turning,
                     double time)
        Drives the robot for time with provided inputs.
        Parameters:
        forward - The forward driving speed (left joystick)
        turning - The turning speed (right joystick)
        time - The duration of time for driving. If 0 then the robot will drive infinitely.

      • ArcadeDriveWithInputs

        public ArcadeDriveWithInputs(double forward,
                     double turning,
                     double time,
                     boolean autoSteer)
        Drives the robot for time with provided inputs, optionally driving straight using a gyro.
        Parameters:
        forward - The forward driving speed (left joystick)
        turning - The turning speed (right joystick)
        time - The duration of time for driving. If 0 then the robot will drive infinitely.
        autoSteer - Whether to attempt to drive straight (using a gyro)
